{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b911f4bb9a","title":"对郭化若来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4fb7621f26","index":0,"year":1973,"month":8,"day":4,"articleId":"b911f4bb9a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[{"id":"cb693eeadb","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"b911f4bb9a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"总理，指周恩来。剑英，即叶剑英，当时任中共中央军委副主席兼极书长，主持军委日常工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8d715f86af","type":"title","text":"对郭化若来信”的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"b911f4bb9a"},{"id":"cb693eeadb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理、剑英同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"b911f4bb9a"},{"id":"612daee098","type":"paragraph","text":"请考虑可否给郭化若分配工作。并希将孙子序言改版，写一篇批判吸收性的序言。此信并请告郭。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"b911f4bb9a"},{"id":"59ecb3de34","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"b911f4bb9a"},{"id":"d5c8c3ad54","type":"paragraph","text":"73，8，4","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"b911f4bb9a"},{"id":"f15a963312","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]郭化若，原任中国人民解放军南京军区第一副司令员。“文化大革命”中受到错误批判。1973年7月20日，他给毛泽东写信，讲到自己“在介绍《孙子兵法》时写了错误严重的《代序》”“任意夸张《孙子》，把《孙子》现代化”“又不积极修改赶早改版”。信中还向毛泽东请求分配工作。同年，郭化若出任中国人民解放军军事科学院副院长。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"b911f4bb9a"}],"page":{"id":"d379950742","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"b911f4bb9a","start":434,"end":434}}}},"__N_SSG":true}